{{Quote|By authority of the Diktat of Corellia and in recognition of outstanding service to the Corellian Security Force, it is my honor to present to you the Corellian Medal of Distinguished Service.|[[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Mack Jasper|Jasper]], to a spacer|<ref name="SWG:RtToaGD" />}}
The '''Medal for Distinguished Service''' was a medal awarded by the [[Diktat]] of [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] for "''distinguished service to [[Corellian Security Force|CorSec]] and the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]''."

==History==
{{Quote|You have done us a great service this day, and it is my honor to recognize that service with the Corellian Medal of Distinguished Service!|[[Diktat]] [[Daclif Gallamby]], to a spacer|<ref name="SWG:RtToaGD" />}}
After the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], Diktat [[Daclif Gallamby]] awarded the medal to a spacer who discovered and foiled a plot arranged by the [[Rogue CorSec]] to discredit the government and overthrow the Diktat.<ref name="SWG:RtToaGD" />

==Behind the scenes==
This was a player reward in ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'' for completing the [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] arc of the post-Legacy quest-line.<ref name="SWG:RtToaGD" />

